      "content": "i know i should talk to someone but it doesn't change anything. the house is just empty. everything feels so pointless now. even getting out of bed feels like a huge chore. it's like there's no reason to even keep trying when the one thing that made it all worth it is just gone. i just want the hurting to stop.",
